        "rich_text_8DL9Df": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "introduction",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>When exploring the world of fine jewellery, you'll encounter various gold purities. Among them, 9 karat gold stands out as a popular choice for its unique blend of beauty, durability, and affordability. But what is 9kt gold, really? At Lucira Jewelry, we believe in accessible luxury and transparent choices. This guide will demystify<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/9kt-collection\" target=\"_blank\" title=\" 9kt gold\"> 9kt gold</a>, helping you understand why this metal is a brilliant option for crafting modern, timeless pieces designed for everyday elegance especially when paired with our stunning<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/lab-grown-diamond-rings\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">lab grown diamond rings</span></a>.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_bUfHBT": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Decoding 9kt Gold: The Basics of Purity and Composition",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Decoding 9kt Gold: The Basics of Purity and Composition</h2>",
            "custom_id": "decoding",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_QakwKa": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Decoding 9kt Gold: Paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Understanding what is 9kt gold starts with its composition. Unlike pure gold, which is too soft for jewellery, gold is mixed with other metals to create a stronger, more resilient alloy. The purity of this alloy is measured in karats (kt).</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_JmwFBb": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "What Does the '9kt' Hallmark Actually Mean?",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>What Does the '9kt' Hallmark Actually Mean?</h3>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_9KgCcw": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/What_Does_the_9kt_Hallmark_Actually_Mean_068c91c0-9a85-4655-af96-28ebc946ced0.png",
            "text": "<p>The term 'karat' denotes the purity of gold out of 24 parts. Therefore, 9kt gold is a carefully crafted blend that consists of:</p><ul><li>9 parts pure gold<br/></li><li>15 parts other alloy metals</li></ul>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": true,
            "products": [
              "0-252ct-half-eternity-prong-diamond-band",
              "glowing-swirl-diamond-ring"
            ]
          }
        },
        "rich_text_DybT3W": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "What Does the '9kt' Paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>This composition means that 9kt gold contains 37.5% pure gold. In India and across the world, you'll often find it stamped with a '375' hallmark a certified mark that guarantees its purity. At Lucira, all our jewellery carries a BIS hallmark, assuring you of its authenticity and quality.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_Jc4E4r": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "The Alloy Metals That Give 9kt Gold Its Strength",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>The Alloy Metals That Give 9kt Gold Its Strength</h2>",
            "custom_id": "the-alloy",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_AWtNat": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/The_Alloy_Metals_That_Give_9kt_Gold_Its_Strength.png",
            "text": "<p>The 15 parts of other metals, or alloys, are crucial. They not only provide strength but also influence the gold's final color. Common alloys include:</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": true,
            "products": [
              "celestial-cluster-diamond-stud-earrings",
              "baguette-round-diamond-harmony-ring"
            ]
          }
        },
        "rich_text_k9U7ew": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<ul><li>Copper: Adds durability and a warm, rosy hue.</li><li>Silver: Contributes to strength and can create a paler yellow or white gold.</li><li>Zinc: Used to enhance durability and prevent tarnishing.</li></ul>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_PmXWVq": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "The Alloy Metals That Paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>By adjusting the proportions of these metals, jewellers can create different shades like yellow, white, and rose gold offering a versatile palette for every design.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_xii4nX": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "The Great Debate: Is 9kt Gold Good for Your Jewelry Collection?",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>The Great Debate: Is 9kt Gold Good for Your Jewelry Collection?</h2>",
            "custom_id": "the-great",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_rPmLpx": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "The Great Debate: Is Paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>One of the most common questions we hear is, <em>“Is 9kt gold good for jewelry?”</em> The answer is a resounding yes, particularly for those who value both practicality and elegance. It strikes an excellent balance between luxury and everyday wearability.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_kjgWbP": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "The Case for Durability and Affordability",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>The Case for Durability and Affordability</h3><p>The higher alloy content makes 9kt gold incredibly durable. Here’s why it’s a smart choice:</p><ul><li>Superior Strength: It is significantly harder and more resistant to scratches and dents compared to 18kt or 22kt gold.<br/></li><li>Perfect for Everyday Wear: Its robustness makes it ideal for pieces you wear daily, like engagement rings, delicate pendants, and bracelets.<br/></li><li>Accessible Luxury: The lower pure gold content makes the price of 9kt gold much more accessible, allowing you to own beautifully crafted fine jewelry without a hefty price tag. To make it even easier, Lucira’s <em>Vault Of Dreams</em>  savings plan helps you plan your purchase smartly.</li></ul>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_rQKzCe": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Considerations for Sensitive Skin and Long-Term Value",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Considerations for Sensitive Skin and Long-Term Value</h3><p>While the higher alloy content is great for durability, some people with very sensitive skin might be concerned about potential reactions. However, <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lucira Jewelry\">Lucira Jewelry</a> mitigates this by using high-quality, often nickel-free alloys to ensure comfort. The long-term value of 9kt gold lies not just in its gold content but in its longevity and craftsmanship. When asking if 9kt gold is good, consider its lasting power as a piece you can wear and cherish for years.</p>",
            "custom_id": "comparison",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_ADDTPa": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Appearance, Colour, and Durability: A Closer Look",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Appearance, Colour, and Durability: A Closer Look</h2><p>Understanding the visual and physical properties of 9kt gold helps in making an informed decision. Let's explore the signature look of 9kt yellow gold and tackle the common concern about tarnishing.</p>",
            "custom_id": "appearance",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_WrWc6F": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "What is 9kt Yellow Gold and Its Signature Hue?",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>What is 9kt Yellow Gold and Its Signature Hue?</h3><p>So, what is 9kt yellow gold specifically? Its appearance is a beautiful, subtle pale yellow. This delicate hue is less intense than the deep, rich yellow of higher karats, which many find more versatile and modern. Its softer color complements a wide range of skin tones and pairs exquisitely with the brilliant sparkle of Lucira’s<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/modern-diamond-earrings-design\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">modern diamond earrings design </span></a>creating a refined look perfect for any occasion.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_mrwtrW": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Does 9kt Gold Tarnish and How to Prevent It?",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Does 9kt Gold Tarnish and How to Prevent It?</h3><p>A key question for many is, <em>does 9kt gold tarnish?</em> Pure gold itself does not tarnish. However, the alloy metals, particularly copper, can react with oxygen and moisture over time, which may cause slight discoloration or tarnish. The good news is that this is a very slow process and is easily managed.</p><p>To keep your Lucira pieces shining:</p><p>1]Avoid contact with harsh chemicals like chlorine, perfumes, and cleaning agents.<br/>2]Remove your jewelry before swimming or showering.<br/>3]Store it in a dry, safe place, like the box it came in.<br/><br/>With minimal care, your 9kt gold jewelry will maintain its brilliance for a lifetime.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_7bxGmb": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Understanding the Price of 9kt Gold in India",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Understanding the Price of 9kt Gold in India</h2>",
            "custom_id": "understanding",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_84HmnH": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Understanding the Price Paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>The affordability of 9kt gold is one of its most attractive features. The 9kt gold price in India is significantly lower than that of 18kt or 22kt gold, making fine, ethically sourced jewelry more accessible than ever. This aligns perfectly with Lucira’s mission to reimagine diamonds for modern India.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_LghJCQ": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Key Factors That Determine the 9kt Gold Price in India",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Key Factors That Determine the 9kt Gold Price in India</h3><p>Several factors influence the final price of 9kt gold jewelry:</p><ul><li>Gold Rate: The daily market rate of pure gold.<br/></li><li>Weight: The total gram weight of the piece.<br/></li><li>Making Charges: The cost of craftsmanship, design complexity, and labor.<br/></li><li>Gemstones: The addition of diamonds or other gems.<br/></li></ul><p>At Lucira, by pairing affordable 9kt gold settings with our high-quality, lab-grown diamonds, we offer stunning designs at exceptional value—like our timeless<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/rose-gold-diamond-necklace\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">rose gold diamond necklace</span></a> that blends elegance with everyday wearability.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_CNg3En": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "9kt vs. Higher Karats: Making the Right Choice for You",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>9kt vs. Higher Karats: Making the Right Choice for You</h2><p>Choosing the right karat depends on your lifestyle, budget, and personal preference. The question of what is 9kt gold often leads to comparisons with other popular purities like 18kt gold.</p>",
            "custom_id": "9kt-vs",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_i7QnKX": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/9kt_vs._Higher_Karats_Making_the_Right_Choice_for_You_1080_250.png"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_Y8FQHz": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Discover Sustainable Luxury: Lucira's 9kt Gold & Lab-Grown Diamond Collection",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Discover Sustainable Luxury: Lucira's 9kt Gold & Lab-Grown Diamond Collection</h2>",
            "custom_id": "discover",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_pYwNLB": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Discover_Sustainable_Luxury_Lucira_s_9kt_Gold_Lab-Grown_Diamond_Collection.png",
            "text": "<p>At Lucira, we believe the future of jewellery is both beautiful and ethical. Our choice to feature 9kt gold alongside recycled higher karats aligns perfectly with our commitment to sustainability and modern design. It's the ideal canvas for our ethically sourced, lab-grown diamonds.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": true,
            "products": [
              "antiqua-drop-diamond-stud-earrings",
              "antiqua-drop-diamond-pendant-necklace"
            ]
          }
        },
        "rich_text_DpG4Hn": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Why 9kt Gold is the Perfect Setting for Our Lab-Grown Diamonds",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Why 9kt Gold is the Perfect Setting for Our Lab-Grown Diamonds</h3><p>The synergy between 9kt gold and lab-grown diamonds is undeniable. Here's why they are a perfect match:</p><ul><li>Shared Values: Just as lab-grown diamonds offer a smart, ethical alternative to mined diamonds, 9kt gold provides a practical, durable, and accessible alternative to higher-karat golds.<br/></li><li>Secure Settings: The superior hardness of 9kt gold ensures that your precious diamonds are held securely, providing peace of mind for everyday wear.<br/></li><li>Modern Aesthetic: The subtle hue of 9kt yellow gold complements the brilliant fire of our diamonds without overpowering them, creating a chic, contemporary look.</li></ul>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_R3qDP6": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Customizing Your Dream Design in 9kt Gold with Lucira",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Customizing Your Dream Design in 9kt Gold with Lucira</h2><p>Your jewellery should be a unique expression of you. That’s why Lucira offers over 1,000 customizable designs featuring certified, conflict-free lab-grown diamonds. You can select 9kt gold as the setting for your chosen piece to create something that is both personal and practical. Ready to bring your vision to life? Book a Video Call with our experts or visit our Mumbai store to explore how 9kt gold can be the foundation of your dream jewelry.</p>",
            "custom_id": "customizing",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_VqwCjk": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Caring for Your Lucira 9kt Gold Jewelry",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Caring for Your Lucira 9kt Gold Jewelry</h2><p>Proper care will ensure your 9kt gold jewellery remains beautiful for generations. Given the question of <em>“Does 9kt gold tarnish?”</em> arises from its alloy content, a simple cleaning routine is all that's needed to maintain its sparkle. We stand by our quality with a Lifetime Exchange and Buyback Guarantee, but a little at-home care goes a long way.</p>",
            "custom_id": "caring",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_zgrNdq": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Simple Cleaning and Storage Tips for Lasting Brilliance",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Simple Cleaning and Storage Tips for Lasting Brilliance</h3><p>Follow these steps to clean your jewelry at home:</p><p>1]Mix a few drops of mild dish soap into a bowl of warm water.<br/>2]Soak your jewelry for 15–20 minutes.<br/>3]Gently scrub with a soft-bristled toothbrush to remove any buildup.<br/><br/>Rinse thoroughly with clean water and pat dry with a soft, lint-free cloth.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_dJ6eQy": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Conclusion",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Conclusion</h2><p>9kt gold offers the perfect harmony of strength, style, and value making it an ideal choice for everyday elegance. Its subtle hue, lasting durability, and accessible price make it a favorite for modern jewelry lovers who seek both beauty and practicality. Whether you’re drawn to lab grown diamond rings, modern diamond earrings, or a rose gold diamond necklace, <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/9kt-collection\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"9kt Gold\">9kt gold</a> provides the perfect setting for timeless sophistication.</p>",
            "custom_id": "conclusion",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        }
      },
